You awake in darkness.  Absolute darkness.

This startles you for several reasons.

First, you should be in Polly's bed, propped up against the wooden headboard, as she always leaves you when she heads off for school in the morning.  True, occasionally she stashes you in the toy chest when Mother orders her to clean the room... but even then, it's never so dark in there as it is here.  You can't imagine where you might be that it's THIS dark.

Second, because you shouldn't have been asleep.  You're a rag doll, after all, and dolls don't sleep.  A doll should be ever-vigilant, always alert and ready to protect the child who loves her.  How could you have been so lazy and irresponsible as to fall asleep? What's wrong with you?

Your heart catches in your throat.  Could Polly be in trouble?  Something is wrong, you can just feel it deep in your fluff.  Something is wrong and you're stuck here in the darkness while Polly is somewhere out there... somewhere out there without you!  You've got to find her before anything bad happens!

But first... you've got to figure out where you are...

[First time players, type HELP for help]

You are in darkness.
You can go south.
The room is completely dark. You can't see anything, but your nose is filled with the overwhelming musk of old cloth and mothballs.
> help

> help
Quick Help

- Objects: Try LOOK AT..., SPEAK TO..., TAKE..., OPEN..., GIVE... TO..., USE... ON/WITH...
- Ask: Most characters in the game will have something to say, useful or not. ASK X ABOUT Y to talk to characters about various topics.
- Inventory: See which items you are carrying by typing I, INV or INVENTORY.
- Moving around: Press the compass buttons, or type GO NORTH, SOUTH, E, GO TO...
- Shortcuts: Press the up arrow and down arrow to scroll through commands you have already typed in. Try X... as a shortcut for LOOK AT...
- Credits: To view the game credits, type CREDITS.
WARNING!!: If you are not logged in, Uktextadventures will time out your session if you idle for too long.  For best experience, it is recommended that you log in or, ideally, download the game file.
> x me

> x me
You are a simple ragdoll, sewn together from scraps and tatters and stuffed with cotton fluff.  Your eyes are mismatched buttons and your mouth is a length of red thread sewn to your face in a permanent smile.  A few spools of red yarn sewn into your scalp simulate hair and your dress is little more than a patchwork shift.
