The dining room is dominated by a large dining table draped with a moth-eaten white table cloth.  High-backed chairs line the table, each also covered by a dingy white sheet. The gathering gloom gives the shrouded furniture the appearance of ghosts.  A second marble fireplace is built into the western wall, so that the family could enjoy a roaring fire to set a cozy ambience at dinner parties and family gatherings.

